<D>__{computer, how long until zero atmosphere?}
<C>__{computer}
<P>__{(after a beat)}
<D>__{four minutes, nine seconds.}
<C>__{phil}
<D>__{if we get below 20% atmosphere, the power will shut down!}
<C>__{terri}
<D>__{are you sure?}
<C>__{phil}
<D>__{positive! a vacuum inside the ship would cause a total electrical failure. the nav computers will fry!}
<C>__{mcconnell}
