<D>__{we'll lose all control. we won't be able to fire the engines to capture mars orbit.}
<A>__{just then a computer screen flickers, freezes. phil punches keys with his good hand. what he sees shocks him.}
<C>__{phil}
<D>__{it's already starting. the primary l 1 hub has been smashed. the systems are crashing.}
<A>__{woody looks back at his crew, struggling to project more calm than he really feels.}
<C>__{woody}
<D>__{everybody switch to suit oxygen. we beat this in the simulator, we can do it here. jim, you've got the ship. i'm going eva.}
